b'Temitope Odedoyin'
b'Temitope Eddna Odedoyin is majoring in English and fully concentrating in media and professional writing.\xc2\xa0Apart from writing, she has\xc2\xa0a passion for painting\xc2\xa0and enjoys using watercolors, oil paint, acrylic, charcoal, oil pastel. She also has an interest in creative writing and short stories. She believes that art \xe2\x80\x94 through writing and painting \xe2\x80\x94 is a way of expressing one\xe2\x80\x99s feelings.'
